I'm going out with Courtney today.. I'm still very sore from dance and surfing on Monday, so I'm going to try to talk her out of kayacking or bike riding (even though thats what i should be doing. Idk maybe we'll go to the mall or something... I had 2 glasses of coffee this morning. --.oh yah i ate like 6 ravioli's before bed last night..i was planning [subconscously] to purge them but my mom got home and was wandering about through the house and I knew I couldn't get away with it. Oh well, I WILL DO BETTER TODAY. <3later

Hi this journal is going to be friends only.  As opposed to my other LJ, this is specifically for posting about things few people know about me; my problems and struggles.  I have always had a hard time opening up to people face to face, and have found it quite therapudic and interesting to release my innermost thoughts and feelings this way.  In writing. Hope to be able to relate to somebody <33
